Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Dollar slumps in Europe
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brt6
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Mar 1978
Dollar slump in Europe as Carter faces stubborn Congress over energy. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.